title: The Ultimate Fighter Brazil 02 - Team Nogueira vs Team Werdum
description:
The Ultimate Fighter: Brazil 2 is an installment of the Ultimate Fighting Championship (UFC)-produced reality television series The Ultimate Fighter. This season marked the third time the show was filmed, in its entirety, outside of Las Vegas, Nevada, and the second time it has filmed in Brazil.

This season consisted of 12 episodes and a live finale in Brazil. The season tournament finale, along with the coaches fight, took place on June 8, 2013.[1] The show started filming in November 2012 and was in Portuguese. The season was again produced by Floresta, a Brazilian production company, and aired in Brazil on Globo.
